name: Lead Report
query:
select 
  name as `ID:Link/Lead:100`,
  creation_date as `Date:Date:100`,
  cast(contact_date as Date) as `Next Contact Date:Date:100`,
  lead_name as `Name:Data:200`,
  mobile_no as `Mobile No:Data:150`,
  status as `Lead Status:Data:100`,
  brand as `Brand:Link/Brand:150`,
  item_group as `Item Group:Link/Brand:150`,
  model as `Model:Data:150`,
  sales_man as `Sales Man:Data:150`,
  notes as `Notes:Text:250`
from 
  `tabLead`
where
  ((creation_date between %(from_date)s and %(to_date)s)
  or (cast(contact_date as Date) between %(from_date)s and %(to_date)s))
